Interface JsonpActionHelper<A extends net.customware.gwt.dispatch.shared.Action<R>,R extends net.customware.gwt.dispatch.shared.Result>

  • Type Parameters:
    A - The class of action to be handled.
    R - The class of result to be produced.
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    GetLatLonActionHelper
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GetLatLonActionHelperImpl

    public interface JsonpActionHelper<A extends net.customware.gwt.dispatch.shared.Action<R>,R extends net.customware.gwt.dispatch.shared.Result>
    Implementations of this interface help the DataManager perfom actions. They construct a URL to call from a specific JsonpAction, and create a Result from the Javascript response.
    Author:
    Andrew Green
